"'''Ancient Republic'''" was a [[Music/Legends|song]] by the band [[Deeply Religious]], originally released on the album ''[[Emperor of Air and Darkness]]''. It was presumably a song reflecting on the freedom and virtues of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]], and was thus banned by the [[Imperial Board of Culture]].

